INSERT INTO FAMILY VALUES (NULL, 2,'Sulidae', '670::671', 'World: 9 species; SE Asia: 3 species; Thailand: 2 species; Vietnam: 3 species. Large birds of coastal waters. Plumage black, dark brown & white. Face including skin around eyes, cheek and throat naked. Wings very long, pointed. Tail wedge-shaped. Bill large, pointed, strong, margin toothed. Feet webbed. Body cigar-shaped. Flight strong. Catch fish by diving headfirst into water from air and can dive after fish in short moment. Often in flocks. Sexes alike.', ' ');
